Package model

Package that contains the MVC pattern's model; it handles the state of the application.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Admin
    Admin class represent an user who is the admin of the website.
    DeliveryPoint
    DeliveryPoint class represents a delivery point for the user.
    Encode
    The Encode class provides the encryption of elements
    HeadmasterCustomer
    HeadmasterCustomer class represent an user who is the holder of a musical school; it extends User class and automatically set the type as TITOLARE.
    Payment
    Payment class represents the method of payment of the user.
    Product
    The product class represents the product, with all his attributes.
    ProductInCart
    ProductInCart associate the product that is already added in the cart to an int that indicate the number of that product in the cart.
    ProfessionalCustomer
    ProfessionalCustomer class represent an user who is a professional customer; it extends User class and automatically set the type as PROFESSIONISTA.
    Purchase
    Purchase class represents a purchase done by a user.
    ShoppingCart
    ShoppingCart class represents the shopping cart, that is associated to an user.
    User
    The User class represents whoever wants to connect to the website.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Brand
    Enumeration class of the brands of products.
    LivelloStrumento
    Enumeration class of the difficulty levels of instruments.
    MetodoDiConsegna
    Enumeration class of shipping methods.
    TipoCliente
    Enumeration class of the types of user.
    TipoStrumento
    Enumeration class of the types of instruments.
